 and reliable tool\nfor quantum computing enhanced computational materials science and chemistry,\nand identify open questions for further research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 20:07:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 22:43:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
