y lesion segmentation with an average volume error that is better than\nvisual assessment by human raters, suggesting these methods are mature enough\nfor a large-scale evaluation for use in clinical practice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 10:40:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 15:44:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2020 18:53:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 08:26:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-11"}
